    {
      "headings": [
        {
          "tag": "h1",
          "text": "Automating Food Plan Management & Saving 60% Time with Copilot"
        },
        {
          "tag": "h2",
          "text": "Our Azure experts implemented Copilot to automate the food plan creation and management process for the institutional and large-scale catering operations. The solution led to massive efficiency gains for food plan managers."
        }
      ],
      "paragraphs": [],
      "listItems": [],
      "ctas": [
        {
          "text": "TRANSFORM YOUR FOOD OPERATIONS",
          "href": "#pgForm"
        }
      ],
      "images": [
        {
          "src": "https://azure.folio3.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Time-with-Copilot.webp",
          "alt": null,
          "w": 636,
          "h": 547
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "headings": [],
      "paragraphs": [
        "Home » Copilot Implementation For WFCF Boosts Productivity By 150%"
      ],
      "listItems": [],
      "ctas": [],
      "images": []
    },
    {
      "headings": [
        {
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "Colorado, USA"
        },
        {
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "Food Production"
        },
        {
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "100+"
        },
        {
          "tag": "h2",
          "text": "Food Verification Organization"
        }
      ],
      "paragraphs": [
        "About The Client",
        "An independent food verification company based in Colorado, USA. They house over 100 employees with an annual revenue generation of $ 25.7 M. Thye provide verification, auditing, and certification services to enhance transparency and authenticity in food production practices, covering every aspect of the food supply chain, including farms, ranches, processors, and retailers. This maintains high standards of food safety and sustainability."
      ],
      "listItems": [],
      "ctas": [],
      "images": []
    },
    {
      "headings": [
        {
          "tag": "h2",
          "text": "Challenges Faced"
        },
        {
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "Manual compilation of diverse dietary preferences from numerous sources caused time delays"
        },
        {
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "Manual and iterative meal plan creation with chances of missed alignment with stakeholders’ feedback"
        },
        {
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "Ensuring compliance with the nutritional standards was complex and prone to errors"
        },
        {
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "Inability to adapt to the last-minute changes to dietary requirements, hindering operational agility"
        },
        {
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "The food plan managers had to be involved in the unworthy administrative tasks, which distracted them from strategic planning"
        }
      ],
      "paragraphs": [
        "The food planning managers were burdened with constant manual effort, including fetching dietary inputs, creating weekly meal plans, updating them based on management’s feedback, and ensuring compliance with nutritional data sources, which was not only time-consuming but also led to human errors. They sought a solution that could enable them to respond quickly to changing requirements and make the overall food plan management more efficient."
      ],
      "listItems": [],
      "ctas": [],
      "images": []
    },
    {
      "headings": [
        {
          "tag": "h2",
          "text": "Integrated AI-Powered Solution for Efficient and Accurate Food Planning"
        },
        {
          "tag": "h2",
          "text": "Folio3 implemented a Copilot-powered automation solution to speed up the entire food planning process. The platform utilized the capabilities of Microsoft tools (Teams, Word, and Excel), Azure OpenAI, and Power Platform components, which were effortlessly integrated into the food plan manager’s dail"
        },
        {
          "tag": "h2",
          "text": "The solution encompassed the following Copilot agents and integrations:"
        },
        {
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "Copilot Agent in Teams"
        },
        {
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "Custom Topic Agent"
        },
        {
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "Copilot Agent in Word"
        },
        {
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "Visual Generation"
        },
        {
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "Custom Action Agent"
        },
        {
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "Connected Data Source Integration"
        },
        {
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "Workflow Automation"
        }
      ],
      "paragraphs": [
        "The Copilot agent within Microsoft initiates the food planning process and quickly gathers dietary preferences through an intuitive conversational interface.",
        "A custom-made topic agent that parses and smartly organizes data from various sources to make it structured for subsequent processing.",
        "The organized meal plan data is then fed into the Copilot agent within Microsoft Word that automatically structures the meal plan into a well-defined and professional document.",
        "To promote clarity and stakeholder engagement, the image-generation AI automatically creates engaging visuals of the meal plans.",
        "To manage the iterations based on the feedback, this custom action agent effortlessly refines or updates specific parts of the meal plan using natural language processing prompts.",
        "Pulling crucial nutritional data from verified connected data sources refined the meal plan with accurate and compliant information.",
        "Speeding up administrative workflows (approvals and distribution of finalized food plans) to relevant stakeholders"
      ],
      "listItems": [],
      "ctas": [],
      "images": []
    },
    {
      "headings": [
        {
          "tag": "h2",
          "text": "Integrated AI-Powered Solution for Efficient and Accurate Food Planning"
        },
        {
          "tag": "h2",
          "text": "Folio3 implemented a Copilot-powered automation solution to speed up the entire food planning process. The platform utilized the capabilities of Microsoft tools (Teams, Word, and Excel), Azure OpenAI, and Power Platform components, which were effortlessly integrated into the food plan manager’s dail"
        },
        {
          "tag": "h2",
          "text": "The solution encompassed the following Copilot agents and integrations:"
        },
        {
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "Copilot Agent in Teams"
        },
        {
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "Custom Topic Agent"
        },
        {
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "Copilot Agent in Word"
        },
        {
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "Visual Generation"
        },
        {
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "Custom Action Agent"
        },
        {
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "Connected Data Source Integration"
        },
        {
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "Workflow Automation"
        }
      ],
      "paragraphs": [
        "The Copilot agent within Microsoft initiates the food planning process and quickly gathers dietary preferences through an intuitive conversational interface.",
        "A custom-made topic agent that parses and smartly organizes data from various sources to make it structured for subsequent processing.",
        "The organized meal plan data is then fed into the Copilot agent within Microsoft Word that automatically structures the meal plan into a well-defined and professional document.",
        "To promote clarity and stakeholder engagement, the image-generation AI automatically creates engaging visuals of the meal plans.",
        "To manage the iterations based on the feedback, this custom action agent effortlessly refines or updates specific parts of the meal plan using natural language processing prompts.",
        "Pulling crucial nutritional data from verified connected data sources refined the meal plan with accurate and compliant information.",
        "Speeding up administrative workflows (approvals and distribution of finalized food plans) to relevant stakeholders"
      ],
      "listItems": [],
      "ctas": [],
      "images": []
    },
